            Due to Hurricane Sandy, the state of New Jersey is allowing several alternative voting methods for displaced voters and first responders. First, you can vote at the polling place nearest where you are on Election Day, instead of your home polling place. To find an accessible polling place, go to www.google.com/elections/ed/us/vote. Next, you can cast your ballot…
